### 根据课程ID查询课程信息
GET {{content_host}}/content/course/40


### 根据课程ID查询课程计划
GET {{content_host}}/content/teachplan/117/tree-nodes


### 新增课程计划--章
POST {{content_host}}/content/teachplan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": 74,
  "parentid": 0,
  "grade": 1,
  "pname": "新章名称 [点击修改]"
}


